0.name: ACCEPTANCE_DEADLINE_DATE
0.sql:
SELECT EVENTDATE
FROM  CASEEVENT E, CASES C
WHERE E.CASEID = C.CASEID
AND E.EVENTNO =-6
AND C.IRN = :gstrEntryPoint
ORDER BY E.Cycle DESC

DELETE FROM TRUSTITEM

326.name: DN_AMOUNTS
326.description: This doc-item uses information from Doc Production to identify the correct ActivityHistory and ActivityRequest rows.
326.sql:
Select AR.DEBITNOTENO, AR.DISBAMOUNT, AR.SERVICEAMOUNT, AR.DISBTAXAMOUNT, AR.SERVICETAXAMOUNT, N.NARRATIVETEXT, N1.NARRATIVETEXT
from ACTIVITYREQUEST AR, ACTIVITYHISTORY AH, NARRATIVE N, NARRATIVE N1
where AR.WHENREQUESTED = :p1
and AR.SQLUSER = :p2
and AR.CASEID = CONVERT (int, :p3)
and AR.ACTIVITYCODE = 3204
AND AR.DEBITNOTENO = AH.DEBITNOTENO
AND AH.DISBNARRATIVE = N.NARRATIVENO
AND AH.SERVICENARRATIVE = N1.NARRATIVENO
